WEBVTT

00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:02.747
A long time ago,

00:00:02.771 --> 00:00:04.519
I was a professional animator.

00:00:06.573 --> 00:00:07.723
(Music)

00:00:07.747 --> 00:00:09.653
[Eric Dyer]

00:00:09.677 --> 00:00:10.687
[Animator]

00:00:10.711 --> 00:00:11.861
[Compositor]

00:00:16.425 --> 00:00:18.151
And at night,

00:00:18.175 --> 00:00:20.458
I would make my own experimental films.

00:00:20.482 --> 00:00:21.535
(Music)

00:00:21.559 --> 00:00:26.190
And I was spending a lot of time,
way too much time, in front of a screen

00:00:26.214 --> 00:00:28.909
for work that would be
presented on a screen,

00:00:28.933 --> 00:00:32.656
and I had this great need
to get my hands back on the work again.